Scripts in this folder are intended to be invoked from the following applicable
triggers:
* Event Listeners

However, they may also be invoked by the following triggers:
* Dashboard Gadgets
* Schedulers
* Live Fields - Screen Executors
* Startup / Shutdown
* Workflow Post Functions

Important Note! Events are global. You will likely want to restrict these
scripts to run only if certain other criteria is met (e.g. project=PROJ and
issueType=Bug)
